<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLee.5B.5BJohn_Nelder.7CNelder.2C_John.5D.5D_Pawitan.2C_Yudi2009">Lee, Youngjo; <a href="/wiki/John_Nelder" title="John Nelder">Nelder, John</a> Pawitan, Yudi (2006). <i>Generalized Linear Models with Random Effects: Unified Analysis via H-likelihood</i>. Boca Raton: Chapman and Hall/CRC. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1584886315" class="internal">ISBN 1-584-88631-5</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Generalized+Linear+Models+with+Random+Effects%3A+Unified+Analysis+via+H-likelihood&amp;rft.aulast=Lee&amp;rft.aufirst=Youngjo&amp;rft.au=Lee%2C+Youngjo&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BJohn+Nelder%7CNelder%2C+John%5D%5D+Pawitan%2C+Yudi&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.pub=Boca+Raton%3A+Chapman+and+Hall%2FCRC&amp;rft.isbn=1-584-88631-5&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Generalized_linear_model"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> <a href="http://www.crcpress.com/shopping_cart/products/product_detail.asp?sku=C6315" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.crcpress.com/shopping_cart/products/product_detail.asp?sku=C6315" rel="nofollow">[7]</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
